/-- **Theorem 11.4 global `|LŐā|` row-sum split**.  First-stage and recursive
trailing row-sum caps cover every row of `|LŐā|`, using the same leading/trailing
index split as the `DŐā` and product-entry handoffs. -/
theorem higham11_4_L_row_sum_bound_of_first_stage_recursive_split
    (n s : ‚Ąē) (L_hat : Fin n ‚Üí Fin n ‚Üí ‚ĄĚ) (Lmax localL recL : ‚ĄĚ)
    (hlocal_le : localL ‚Č§ Lmax) (hrec_le : recL ‚Č§ Lmax)
    (hfirst : ‚ąÄ r : Fin n, r.val < s ‚Üí
      (‚ąĎ k : Fin n, |L_hat r k|) ‚Č§ localL)
    (htrail : ‚ąÄ r : Fin n, s ‚Č§ r.val ‚Üí
      (‚ąĎ k : Fin n, |L_hat r k|) ‚Č§ recL) :
    ‚ąÄ r : Fin n, (‚ąĎ k : Fin n, |L_hat r k|) ‚Č§ Lmax := by
  intro r
