    (relativeError p_n u condAx residualTerm : ‚ĄĚ) : Prop :=
  relativeError ‚Č§ p_n * u * condAx + residualTerm

/-! ## ¬ß11.1.4 Tridiagonal matrices -/

/-- **Algorithm 11.6** pivoting parameter
